document.readableText: The universe doesn't notice many things.
If the universe happens to notice something it probably won't remember it anyway.
The universe only remembers problems it doesn't understand. There used to be many things that confused the universe. Now there are 108.
Some of the 108 problems frighten the universe. Epic conflicts and galactic paradoxes could break reality and cause the universe to implode.
The universe reacts severely, defending against these kinds of threats
Some of the 108 problems pose no threat to the universe but still attract its influence. These interactions are not violent but inquisitive in their nature.
In order for the universe to interact with a problem it requires a Wizard. 108 Wizards exist to solve the remaining mysteries of the universe.
The oldest of the 108 remaining Wizards is an Ancient. He is Alfons, the Humble Magnificent. Monster Breaker. The Hand of The Universe. .
Alfons serves the universe in a realm of war and honor, engaging cosmic monstrosities in combat.
The youngest of the Wizards is Ernie... who lives in a more peaceful realm. Ernie massages unicorns and collects the semi-digested covfefe beans they excrete.
The youngest and oldest Wizards in existence have a unique magical bond. They are Linkwizards.
Linkwizards connect all Wizards with the will of the universe. There are dangerous rituals that Linkwizards must perform.
As a sign of trust and respect, Linkwizards bestow soulbound titles of honor upon each other that last for eternity.
You are Ernie Beanfinder. Barista of Wizards. Pooptoucher.
As part of an old Wizard tradition, Elder linkwizards will often bestow a title of humility upon the junior linkwizard.
Soulbound Titles are permanent. Junior linkwizard titles such as "novice" or "student" will later exist alongside new prestigious titles and better ground the Wizard to reality.
But when Alfons labeled Ernie a Pooptoucher... That was just a mean and fucked up thing to do.
